##582 minutes. Papers!

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

By Chen Yiping, thepaper.cn

At about 8:00 p.m. on February 14, Shanghai Municipal Engineering Design and Research Institute Group Co. , Ltd. (hereinafter referred to as "Shanghai Municipal General Institute") received an urgent commission from Wuhan Changjiang New Town Construction Investment Group Co. , Ltd. , to undertake the municipal supporting design work of Wuhan Changjiang New Town Shelter Hospital. According to the plan of prevention and control, the Shanghai Municipal General Hospital should finish the first draft of the design before 6:00 the next morning.

Epidemic is the order, prevention and control is the responsibility. As the municipal infrastructure industry "national team" , the Shanghai Municipal General Hospital immediately replied, "we must complete the design task on time and quality. ". Time is tight, the task is heavy, all the forces of the Shanghai Municipal General Hospital quickly mobilized, at the same time race, with the epidemic, determined to win the "sprint" and "relay race.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Yangtze new town shelter hospital plans to build 20 cabins, a total of more than 3,000 beds. Man Wui network

At 20:18 on February 14, the Shanghai Municipal Government General Hospital (SMHGC) urgently formed 44 teams composed of the heads of the departments and above of the urban traffic and municipal transportation departments, the Fifth Academy, the Construction Cost Company, the Zhengji Company and the Wuhan on-site Departments. Liu Jun, the project manager, looked at his watch. The next morning he had to finish the first draft of the design. The "big test" lasted only 582 minutes. This is a race against time, not a moment to slow down, not a moment to relax.

Under the coordination of Liu Jun's organization, immediately held a Web Conference, Wuhan Branch of the existing construction site collected characteristics and existing conditions for comprehensive analysis. The professional heart to heart, together action, inverted row time, synergy, immediately put into the intensive work.

22:30,450 minutes to due date. The network meeting confirmed the design, roads, construction, structure, cost, water supply, pipelines and sewage collection, solid waste, electrical, monitoring and other professional designers on duty. Including the hospital and the outside of the existing municipal road access road, the hospital sidewalk renovation, lighting and monitoring, sanitary facilities layout, waste water disinfection and disposal, storage and transfer of medical solid waste, disease areas connected to the steel structure of the canopy, such as a clear division of Labor, the design of the project was officially launched.

At 2300 hours, 155 minutes after the "examination" was conducted, the design principles and standards of the supporting facilities for the municipal administration of the Shelter Hospital were discussed, and the plan was combined with the requirements for health protection in temporary special places recently issued by the National Health and Disease Control Bureau, based on the comprehensive consideration of the site construction conditions in Wuhan, and on the premise of ensuring the functional requirements of the Shelter Hospital, the favorable conditions are created for the on-site construction.

At 1:30 a.m. , with only about 270 minutes left, the team encountered challenges in the design process. According to the "technical requirements for design and alteration of Shelter Hospitals" and the related guidance document just released on February 5, special requirements are made for the layout of the building, the process of diagnosis and treatment, and the isolation of the area sign, which are restricted by many boundary conditions. At the same time, the medical equipment load, the weight and load when the equipment moves should be calculated in multiple ways, not only considering the efficiency, but also ensuring the safety.

At this time, several chief teachers involved in the audit joined the working group. When they got the call for help, they threw themselves into their work and did not sound drowsy during the call. Faced with such urgent and special design task, the overall coordination of the project is directly connected with the chief engineer of each specialty to realize system integration and overall control, and strive to optimize the scheme, design optimization synchronous development, soon, design problems readily solved.

At 4:15 in the morning, all the participants of the Shanghai Municipal General Hospital have been fighting for eight hours continuously, they are staring at the screen, afraid of missing any number. Everyone has a string in their hearts, holding a strong, for fear of design details and omissions, for fear of "answer" the time to hand in the paper is getting closer, but they can not squeeze out a watch gap.

At 6:00 a.m. , when the due date came, Liu Jun looked at his watch again and breathed a sigh of relief  as if it had been a sleepless night for the 44 men who fought through the night, finally completed the stage of the construction drawing design task. But the Ark of life-saving construction is urgent, just in time to hand in papers with the virus race midway victory. Fighting the epidemic and making sure the hospital gets built, it's still going to take them a second to relax.

In order to guide the construction with the drawings, the design team of this department provides consultation and suggestion by video conference system, and works on duty in the way of Network all day long. The design team can provide feedback, study and modify the design at any time on the construction site, at the same time, two professional technicians of Wuhan branch are arranged to provide on-site 24-hour cooperation service.

"The scene is handed over to us, comrades-in-arms in Shanghai, Wuhan is not the front line, Wuhan is my home. " On February 15 in Wuhan, an unexpected cold wave came, but Lee Wei and Zhu Wei of the Wuhan Branch, undaunted and unflinching, at 7 a.m, they went out against the sleet. Walk in the morning empty streets, the heart is very hot, to fight the epidemic to contribute, worth it!

In order to ensure the health and safety of technicians on site, the Shanghai Municipal General Hospital established a logistics support group according to the measures for the prevention of the epidemic, the leader pays real-time attention to and strictly controls the work and rest time of each employee so as not to cause the reduction of immunity; must wear goggles, protective masks, protective gloves outside, and wash hands with disinfectant immediately after entering the office or returning home, and spraying and killing the outer clothing, sterilizing and sealing the used disposable protective articles and putting them into the special garbage collection box to avoid secondary pollution; Timely deployment of masks, goggles and other resources to reach the hands of construction staff.
